{"title":"收割水稻","authors":["陈所巨"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":11,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割水稻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈所巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾场碾平扫净之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那温厚产床和碎金子阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就等待从大板箩倾泻的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金瀑布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候我们充满喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们所指望的丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎不只一次幸福地走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们所期待的奇迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎不只一次摆动黄金旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的兄弟姐妹们在汗和雨的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水稻田中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像淘金者淘出金色亮星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那镰刀不仅只是工具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抑或也有感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那稻禾不仅只是植物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抑或也是多情的如愿以偿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们丰厚殷情的大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割从来都是节日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风与土地的回声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光与雨水的梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都只为必然的饱满与丰润吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都只为握住镰刀柄的手吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割水稻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国这片稻米产区"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟与丰收的交响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情不自禁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}